oracle.xml.util

Class QxName

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.xml.namespace.QName
      • oracle.xml.util.QxName
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class QxName
extends javax.xml.namespace.QName
    This class represents the XML Name used in DOM/XSLT and other modules. It consists of Prefix, LocalName, and Namespace and optional QName. The class is immutable.
